{
  "title": "Edgecast Overview",
  "author_name": "Datadog",
  "description": "This dashboard provides a high-level overview of your Edgecast services, so you can view aggregated throughput and latency metrics as well as the cache hit ratio of your CDN.\n\nSee the [Edgecast Documentation](https://docs.datadoghq.com/integrations/edgecast_cdn/) for further reading.\n\n \nClone this template dashboard to make changes and add your own graph widgets.",
